16#include "api/array_view.h"

18namespace webrtc {
19
20// Decides the sample rate of a mixing iteration given the preferred
21// sample rates of the sources.
22class OutputRateCalculator {
23 public:
24 virtual int CalculateOutputRateFromRange(
25 rtc::ArrayView<const int> preferred_sample_rates) = 0;

27 virtual ~OutputRateCalculator() {}
28};
